frames.caption: A mystical elf warrior with long white hair and pointed ears rides a majestic tiger through a dense forest. The elf is clad in intricately designed armor, exuding an aura of strength and mystery. The tiger strides confidently, its eyes fixed forward, as dappled sunlight filters through the canopy above.
